Run - start a container

docker run nginx


Ps - list containers

docker ps
docker ps -a (includes exited container) 


Stop - stop a container

docker stop <name ex. silly_sammet> 


Rm - remove a container

docker rm <name ex. silly_sammet> 
docker rm <id>


Images - list images

docker images
docker image ls 


rmi - Remove images

docker rmi nginx


Pull - download an image

docker pull nginx


Exec - execute a command

(Ubuntu container)
docker exec <name or container id> cat /etc/hosts


Run - attach and detach

docker run kodekloud/simple-webapp
docker run -d kodekloud/simple-webapp
docker attach <id ex. a043d>

Run - interactive to OS container

docker run -it centos bash

